axy color distributions, as a function of\nluminosity and as a function of richness, in the model and in the two group\ncatalogs. Except for faint galaxies and small groups, the model and both group\ncatalogs are in very good agreement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 May 2008 20:10:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Oct 2008 19:24:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
