line of a generalized field theory on\nthe tangent bundle $TM$ of $M$\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 May 2008 12:13:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 27 Sep 2008 15:59:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 1 Aug 2009 19:08:27 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 5 Aug 2009 05:54:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
